l-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9b%2FMachete_Kills_2013.jpg&h=0de9180c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b3/Gone_in_Sixty_Seconds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb3%2FGone_in_Sixty_Seconds.jpg&h=352de720&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/15/Burnt_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F15%2FBurnt_Poster.jpg&h=1214d896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事圍繞墨西哥人科爾特斯（丹尼&middot;特喬）展開，講述他在墨西哥和自己的兄弟們拯救那些被綁架的女孩子們的故事。<br />\n<br />\n2.該片承接《絕煞刀鋒》故事，自從墨西哥人科爾特斯（丹尼&middot;特喬）幹掉德克薩斯州的黑幫之後，聲名日隆，被美國總統任命為特使，負責追殺一個卡特爾組織從墨西哥越過邊境來到美國的恐怖分子...<br />\n<br />\n3.六年前，竊車界中綽號「曼菲斯」的藍道雷恩斯，乃是一位技術頂尖的偷車賊，不但行竊過程從來未曾失手過，最快的行竊速度紀錄是六十秒，而且法律無法制裁他。但是，曼菲斯的母親十分擔心他弟弟藍道奇普會受到他影響，而步上後塵，勸戒他能就此停手，毅然從竊車界中退休，過著平凡的生活..<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述亞當&middot;瓊斯是一名有著好手藝的帥氣廚師，但因使用毒品和其古怪脾氣而讓他失去了自己的餐廳；他試圖重新找回他的生活和職業生涯，而在倫敦開一家新餐廳，並帶領著一支團隊，希望贏得米其林三星、引進新的烹調方式Sous Vide（低溫真空烹調）；這是把原料烹調到最佳熟成度，再加工調理出前所未有的美味，使他準備再度重回高峰<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=b24588c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=047cf27b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ed822b74ebad47cd932a51dedd36abc6d7a8f7","tid":1171054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T12:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bea783361e83611988005105db592dfcc18cf2","tid":1171054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518c3321ffdafae4e0b675588af0cab7e774f6ba","tid":1171054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2110036567d972abde8e44e3d67b0052d5728862","tid":1171054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace97f1acf0e12d0bd36d08c52792b99dbc5ec2f","tid":1171054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99931cbf096d6950a4b0c4889291e6d8d3f41345","tid":1171054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fed3bca8d015a5e9f20131ceba3b6cf2ff7f6d2","tid":1171054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco